Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?" I am like "What the hack? I'm dying!" and the bee says "I'm not going to let you die, my Queen. I'm here to save you." I'm like "What?" and the bee says "I'm a bee servant, your Majesty." I asked "A bee servant?" and the bee says "Yes, I'm a bee that was born with the ability to understand human speech. Just give me commands" I'm like "I don't know what to say" and the bee says "Just say anything, my Queen." I'm excited and say "Okay, I want a sandwich" and the bee says "Yes, my Queen." It then flips its wings many times and a delicious sandwich appears before me. I eat it and it tastes like the best sandwich I've ever had. I'm like "This is amazing!" and the bee says "I'm glad you like it, my Queen."
